Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:26.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Wake up into this nightmare that will never end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.55,0:01:31.06,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}The main attraction of this twisted master plan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:48.30,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I will be your deadman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:52.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}With nothing but this blood on my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:57.14,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in your Wonderland
