Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:26.72,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,505)\pos(990,550)\blur1}#03   G 栋

Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃 丸太觉得如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会再一起吃点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 也许…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就要被执行死刑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的Race太吓人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体处理班都总动员了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要中途退出 也很难做到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得那么夸张 却没优胜者 简直莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我没参加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个Race的难度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用下半身想都知道有蹊跷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是参加了 想必现在也已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个新人 五十岚丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为他参加了才变成那样的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致美美的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有留遗书的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以决定写给美美父亲您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许您不会相信我所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是杀了美美和山炸排 还有班里其它人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天就要被执行死刑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你是这间囚室的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我们是室友 真是太巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找你噢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是「Candy」?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我撞倒了你 才弄丢的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我需要负责
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是总算弄到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你一定要收下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下 我就还能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 羊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一辈子都不会忘记你的大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情不这么发展 我才为难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我不惜受重伤才弄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那个创办人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟为何对这家伙那么执着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我监视这次来的新人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然报酬是不会亏待你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么细节都可以 只要有什么动作或是变化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来向我报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需要什么说明吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只需要CastPoint
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的模范囚犯已经没有了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 笼络了他 没什么坏处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 难吃的传闻可是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 去吃点什么清清口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Mather Goose System」停止运行了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(587,663)}Wretched Egg
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}原罪脱逃?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 创办人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检修时 貌似发生了原因不明的error
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提前0.1秒也好 快给我重启
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(554,661)}Wretched Egg
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}在原罪笑出來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 没钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买单啦 作为友谊的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 真是把全班同学都杀了的（疯子）吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 越是这种家伙就越难讲…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然想起了以前的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许 那时 我真的很快乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 丸太 没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红衣…男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙卷风? 爆炸?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 究竟怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来杀我的朋友了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是「罪之枝」的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个混蛋!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从手里射出了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑 混蛋 站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Mather Goose System」修复
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}确认了原罪的波动干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(598,659)}Wretched Egg
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(504,661)}Wretched Egg
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}原罪捕获部队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁 这果然不是巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的住人诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 这报酬太少了 那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个红色的家伙也是 这群怪物怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 这血肉欢腾的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的「死囚乐园」

Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊啊啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在睡 我不留神把你的点心也吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说庭院里发生了恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是恐怖袭击?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我 突然胸口刺痛 然后用了奇怪的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那家伙类似的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 红衣男 那混蛋就在这所监狱里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我能射出那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红衣…男?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 那时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么 我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的 全身戴满了奇怪束缚器具的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 以前也有见过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几年前 一个家伙像那样 使出了诡异的龙卷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把工厂的墙都吹跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那家伙现在还被关在一个叫G栋的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G栋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红衣男 就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的朋友都杀掉了的 那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「利落」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于之前的骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对外声称是激进派人权保护团体所策划的炸弹袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那犯人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉木创办人称 「此案已结」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不清楚那只老狐狸想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我另有线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要参考人 就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5580号 是那个孩子么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙有种奇怪的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.42,0:12:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不叫人联想到他带有什么强力的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 莳名看守长 这也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非这武器藏在他体内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的荣耀就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维护这座死囚乐园的安全和秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一味地得过且过消极度日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动代号是「All Red」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迅速到位地将其捉拿归案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看守长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不会是要用那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急状态下使用代号的意义 不懂么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让我们停止无谓的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而更迅速地完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急封锁各处设施
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安保装置「Necro Macro」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,序列锁 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认密码 2DOD 7785
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前曾因一名囚犯闹事而使用过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因此造成死伤24人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 将它视为不可使用之物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是担心那孩子会导致更多的牺牲者?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}现在下达禁止外出令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}所有的工作人员和服刑者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}请迅速回到自己的房间和监牢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}保持待命 直至紧急状态解除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}此外 5580号请即刻前来报到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳名长官也真是的 太小题大做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太要是变成废品的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个监视者要如何负责呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰见羊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能有能力去照看那些怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群人到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红斗篷男人已经被顺利逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为丸太是被邀请前往真正死囚乐园的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要好好地对他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也觉得这么做不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}5580号请即刻前来报到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}重复5580号请即刻前来报道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5580号 是在叫我么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 丸太 你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 是跑步比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是因为启用了最高级的安保措施
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你要是无视报到命令的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会像我一样被惩罚的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后别再给我出问题了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊 对不起 我赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在比赛跑步哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊你也看到了吧 那个红衣男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那种奇怪的能力把我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我所有朋友一个不留地都杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说 这里的犯人逃出去杀人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事怎么可能发生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说那家伙在G栋的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我 必须过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G栋? 没有这个地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这里监牢的构造　只有A到F的六个部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 G栋什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 比起这个　你还是快去报到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G栋?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G那里我能去哦　我知道有条捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么 白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你撅什么嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的话 就告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是安保机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是来抓你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白 捷径呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我搞不懂你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白酱?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微推一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能从这里去很多地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微?…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认目标为5580号和9061号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小偷也在一起么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那机器人要杀了我们么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些看守打算干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 这里！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停 停下了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊 你刚才做什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手贱是我的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手贱?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始 在生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是G栋?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红衣男就在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去目标反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Necro Macro」也失去反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳名看守长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能全都突然消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示在这死囚乐园中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在不属于我管辖的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只老狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已经来到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊 白 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把毫无关系的你们俩扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点没错 现在说太迟了 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太是个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然去踹机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是毫无关系的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫大家都被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我趁丸太你睡着的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了你的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是丸太你的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是生这个的气么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦 你快下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待那里的话很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样么 我…又交到了新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}丸太 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 住手 你这块破铜烂铁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那个力量 使用那个力量的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现啊 出现啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不出现啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:21:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「利落」
